### Login as ADMIN
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@battery-mes.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Login as OPERATOR
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "operator@battery-mes.com",
  "password": "Operator123!"
}

### Login as INSPECTOR
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "inspector@battery-mes.com",
  "password": "Inspector123!"
}

### Replace {{token}} with the accessToken from login

### Lots
GET http://localhost:8080/api/lots?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Work Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/work-orders?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Equipment
GET http://localhost:8080/api/equipment?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Inspections
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inspections?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Defects
GET http://localhost:8080/api/defects?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard KPI
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/kpis
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}